visual_description.name: cyclists_group_meal_stone_cabin.jpg
visual_description.description: Large group of cyclists in matching jerseys eating at a long table with red checkered cloth. Cabin with stone walls, white wooden beams. Daylight, mixed lighting. Cluttered composition.
visual_description.score_basis: Image captures a cheerful social moment. Resolution decent but lighting uneven. Some areas overexposed, messiness on table. Faces slightly obscured, tight framing. Composition crowded, not visually balanced.
